Quote: We as labor force, are even cheaper than those raffle tickets.
Author: popoway

Quote: Not every day is meant to be good, but we live every day to reach the good.
Author: Ms. N

Quote: What’s worse than a dongle? No dongle.
Author: The Verge

Quote: Don’t get distracted by what’s in front of you and pursue the wrong prey.
Author: Shuichi Akai

Quote: It’s like an vending machine for canned juice. You’ll get what you want so long as you have the money, but you get nothing in return without it. You can’t buy your way into the hearts of others.
Author: Ai Haibara
